author: arj
msg: Recently added status flags for UserCheckTag were moved to UserProfileTag and renamed. The new property values are "canChangePassword" and "canChangeLoginName" and are used in ProfileTab.jsp to selectively display input fields. These properties also allow negation too (e.g., !canChangePassword).
